snippet.title: Hot Lava [Official Launch Trailer]
snippet.description:
Play Hot Lava now on Apple Arcade:
https://apple.co/-HotLava

Play Hot Lava now on Steam:
https://store.steampowered.com/app/382560/Hot_Lava/

The Floor is Hot Lava! Run, jump, climb, and surf across nostalgia-packed environments flooded with hot molten lava. Explore alone, or join your friends. But whatever you do, don’t touch the floor.

Music by Muzzy courtesy of Monstercat.
https://www.monstercat.com/artist/muzzy

The Apple logo and Apple Arcade are trademarks of Apple Inc., registered in the U.S. and other countries. Apple Arcade is a service mark of Apple Inc.
